<li><a href="#ch2">Chapter 2: How to Diagnose Core Update Damage in 48 Hours</a></li>
<li><a href="#ch3">Chapter 3: Case Study — B2B SaaS Blog, 28% Traffic Loss to Full Recovery</a></li>
