    <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="step-1-confirm-the-timing">
      <span class="faq-q-text">Step 1: Confirm the Timing</span>
      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="step-1-confirm-the-timing"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Cross-reference your traffic drop with Google's <a href="https://status.search.google.com/">Search Status Dashboard</a>. If the dates do not align, you are looking at a different issue.</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="step-2-segment-your-losses">
