      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="step-2-segment-your-losses"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Export your top 100 pages from Google Search Console. Compare average positions for the 2 weeks before the update versus the 2 weeks after.</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="step-3-analyze-the-winners">
